---
// Testimonials component — Phase H
---

<section id="testimonials" class="testimonials" data-animate>
  <div class="testimonials__container">
    <span class="testimonials__overline">WHAT CLIENTS SAY</span>

    <h2 class="testimonials__headline">Don't Take Our Word for It.</h2>

    <div class="testimonials__grid">
      <!-- Card 1 — Her Ruiz -->
      <div class="testimonials__card" data-animate style="transition-delay: 0s">
        <div class="testimonials__stars" aria-label="5 out of 5 stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
        <p class="testimonials__quote">I run a commercial cleaning and building maintenance company that services offices in Van Nuys, CA and surrounding areas. Before working with Edward, I had no online presence at all— no website, no way for clients to find me or book us online. He built a professional website and set up a booking system so office managers can request quotes and schedule cleanings directly from their phone or computer, any time of day. Now new clients regularly find us online, send booking requests through the site. Recommend.</p>
        <span class="testimonials__name">Her Ruiz</span>
        <span class="testimonials__verified">Verified Google Review</span>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2 — Rosa Vaquera -->
      <div class="testimonials__card" data-animate style="transition-delay: 0.1s">
        <div class="testimonials__stars" aria-label="5 out of 5 stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
        <p class="testimonials__quote">Edward helped me with my website and made the whole process simple and clear. He was responsive, easy to work with, and explained things in a way I understood. Highly recommend.</p>
        <span class="testimonials__name">Rosa Vaquera</span>
        <span class="testimonials__verified">Verified Google Review</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="testimonials__summary">
      <p class="testimonials__rating">&#11088;&#11088;&#11088;&#11088;&#11088; 5.0 on Google</p>
      <p class="testimonials__earn">We earn every review.</p>
      <a href="https://www.google.com/search?q=Reyna+House+AI" class="testimonials__google-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">View on Google &rarr;</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .testimonials {
    background-color: var(--cream);
    padding: 100px 24px;
  }

  .testimonials__container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .testimonials__overline {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    color: var(--copper);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .testimonials__headline {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    color: var(--navy);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .testimonials__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  /* Testimonial card */
  .testimonials__card {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 32px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    text-align: left;
  }

  .testimonials__stars {
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .testimonials__quote {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    color: var(--navy);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .testimonials__name {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    color: var(--copper);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .testimonials__verified {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    color: var(--tan);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  /* Summary section below cards */
  .testimonials__summary {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .testimonials__rating {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    color: var(--navy);
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .testimonials__earn {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    color: var(--tan);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .testimonials__google-link {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--copper);
    border: 2px solid var(--copper);
    padding: 10px 24px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    transition: background-color 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .testimonials__google-link:hover {
    background-color: var(--copper);
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .testimonials__google-link:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid var(--copper);
    outline-offset: 2px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .testimonials__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
